Lutheran Cemetery (old) south side of Metropolitan Ave, opposite 70th Street, showing the chapel in cemetery grounds. View No. 1 is looking northeast, and shows the rear. No. 2 shows the front of the chapel and is viewed northwest; No. 3 also shows the front viewed southwest; No. 4 shows a rear and side view looking southeast.

October 1923.

View 3: 1922.
View 4: October 1923.
